name Pashto (Yusufzai)
language ps-x-yusufzai
language ps 5
maintainer Hanif Rahman <hanifkhan@gmail.com>
status testing
speed 90

// Yusufzai / northeastern Pashto (Peshawar valley), following the dialect
// columns of Wikipedia Help:IPA/Pashto. Relative to the southwestern
// (Kandahari) base ps voice:
//   ښ [ʂ] → [x]     ږ [ʐ] → [ɡ]
//   څ [t͡s] → [s]    ځ [d͡z] → [z]
//   ژ [ʒ] → [d͡ʒ]
// The replace rules convert the shared dictionary post-lookup.
replace 00 S. x
replace 00 Z. g
replace 00 ts s
replace 00 dz z
replace 00 Z dZ
